# 02 - Research Pipeline
# Multi-step research with sequential goals

NAME research-pipeline
INPUT topic
INPUT depth DEFAULT "comprehensive"

GOAL research "Research $topic at a $depth level. Find key facts, history, and current developments."
GOAL analyze "Analyze the research findings. Identify patterns, controversies, and gaps in knowledge."
GOAL synthesize "Synthesize everything into a clear, structured report with sections and bullet points. Save the final report to research-output.md."

RUN pipeline USING research, analyze, synthesize
